@scenario.begin
@contract=presenceJoinWithAnError @na=rust Scenario: Recovery from one unexpected error along the way Given the demo keyset with Presence EE enabled ... passed in 0.021s Given heartbeatInterval set to '1', timeout set to '60' and suppressLeaveEvents set to 'false' ... passed in 0.000s Given a linear reconnection policy with 3 retries ... passed in 0.000s When I join 'first', 'second', 'third' channels with presence ... passed in 0.002s Then I wait for getting Presence joined events ... passed in 3.006s And I observe the following Events and Invocations of the Presence EE: ... passed in 0.000s | type | name | | event | JOINED | | invocation | HEARTBEAT | | event | HEARTBEAT_FAILURE | | invocation | DELAYED_HEARTBEAT | | event | HEARTBEAT_SUCCESS | | invocation | CANCEL_DELAYED_HEARTBEAT | | invocation | WAIT |
@scenario.end --------------------------------------------------------------------------------

@scenario.begin
